28/03/2006
ROME, Italy -- Pope Benedict XVII hopes to promote better understanding and dialogue between the West and Islam during his visit to Turkey in late November, a senior cardinal, Walter Kasper, said on Monday (27 March). The visit is also aimed at strengthening ties with the Orthodox Church, whose ecumenical patriarch, Bartholomew, is based in Istanbul. (Kathimerini - 28/03/06; Reuters - 27/03/06)
